span.p: A0: Функція системи - Управління аптечною системою

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
A0: Управління аптечною системою
Outputs: Orders, Confirmations, Reports
Inputs: Product Data, User Inputs, Payments
Controls: Policies, Business Rules, Tax rules
Mechanisms: React Frontend, Express Backend, Firebase, Payment Gateway

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
A1: Управління каталогом
(Inputs: New/Updated Product Data)
Controls: Categories/Policies
Mechanisms: Admin UI, Firestore
Outputs: Product Listings, Updated Inventory

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
A2: Аутентифікація та профіль
(Inputs: Login/Register Data)
Controls: Auth policies
Mechanisms: Firebase Auth
Outputs: Auth Tokens, User Profiles

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
A3: Кошик та оформлення
(Inputs: Cart Items, Address, Payment Info)
Controls: Stock/Payment Rules
Mechanisms: Frontend, Backend, Payment Gateway
Outputs: Payment Transactions, Checkout Requests

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
A4: Обробка замовлень
(Inputs: Checkout Requests)
Controls: Order Policies
Mechanisms: Backend, Firestore
Outputs: Orders, Status Updates, Emails

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
A5: Керування інвентарем
(Inputs: Orders, Incoming stocks)
Controls: Inventory rules
Mechanisms: Admin Tools, Firestore
Outputs: Inventory Updates, Restock Alerts

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
A6: Повідомлення та звітність
(Inputs: Orders, User actions)
Controls: Notification templates
Mechanisms: Email Service, Firestore
Outputs: Emails, Admin Reports
